In this instalment of the Sunday Times Politics Weekly podcast, journalists Zingisa Mvumvu, Aphiwe De Klerk, Zimasa Matiwane and Amil Umraw discuss the number of allegations made against Malusi Gigaba. Sihle Zikalala seems to be losing his political grip in KwaZulu-Natal, his relationship with Cyril Ramaphosa is discussed.  Tito Mboweni, has made public statements that warrant closer inspection, his strategy is also discussed.